means.exampleOri: That dress must have cost a bomb!
means.exampleTrans: 저 드레스는 돈이 엄청 들었을 거야!

means.value: Seize the night. (→ Work hard, play hard. 고된 하루를 보낸 후에는 좀 즐겨라.)  (opp. Carpe diem.)

means.exampleOri: These animals only come out at night.
Let’s go out on Saturday night.

means.value: 저녁, 밤, 야간(오후 6시경부터 잠자리에 들 때까지의 시간) (→good evening)

items.expExample1: The dog was chained up for the night.
He spent all night at the gaming tables.
He works at night and sleeps during the day.
She peered out into the blackness of the night.
Doctors performed an emergency operation for appendicitis last night.
items.expExample2: 의사들이 지난밤에 응급 맹장 수술을 했다.
